title: Cosmin Mărginean
text: Cosmin Nicolae Mărginean (born 21 November 1978) is a <a href="Romania">Romania</a>n former <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. In his career Mărginean played for <a href="FC%20O%C8%9Belul%20Gala%C8%9Bi">Oțelul Galați</a>, <a href="FC%20Unirea%20Urziceni">Unirea Urziceni</a>, <a href="FC%20Delta%20Dobrogea%20Tulcea">Delta Tulcea</a> and <a href="Kazakhstan">Kazakh</a> club <a href="FC%20Okzhetpes">Okzhetpes</a>.
